{"tid":2211332,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"警員伍尚國稱被「起底」入稟要求移除相關資訊及賠償","createTime":"2020-09-21T05:15:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-21T23:50:43.000Z","uid":20933,"like":18,"dislike":38,"uniUserReply":81,"replies":[{"pid":"fac176bd0333968bca20b9fece1ca6ce1fd23706","tid":2211332,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T05:15:02.000Z","msg":"有警員上周五（18日）入稟高等法院稱遭人「起底」，要求對方移除有關資訊，以及作出賠償。<br />\n<br />\n原告為伍尚國，被告為伍灝賢。入稟狀指出，被告今年6月6日至10日，在其facebook和Instagram發布原告的個人資料，包括中英文全名、相片、地址、警隊和童軍職級，意圖威嚇、侮辱或騷擾原告。<br />\n<br />\n原告要求被告在上述社交媒體中移除有關資訊，同時限制被告發布或公開原告的個人資料；威嚇、侮辱或騷擾原告，以及協助、鼓勵或煽惑他人作出有關行為。"},{"pid":"872b247612779f5f7170a16e76a8f43c770ff7ea","tid":2211332,"uid":20933,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T05:15:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20200921/s00001/1600662874896/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20200921%2Fs00001%2F1600662874896%2F&d=nIll2RoSQXmni3IMQi%2BZoh5ZC4%2B%2BlHDPeg0yH0hWprM%3D&h=1c7bab1e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20200921%2Fs00001%2F1600662874896%2F&h=644084a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20200921/s00001/1600662874896/</a>"},{"pid":"8e4ec646d187b109e250a0fdf3a8f1521375ecb0","tid":2211332,"uid":20933,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T05:16:14.000Z","msg":"千祈唔好Google 伍尚國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d27d4cfab6fe43dbe4ba29e00fb6dc28e9611bcd","tid":2211332,"uid":81353,"like":42,"dislike":0,"score":42,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T05:17:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47ed44eb3e99708db47e90692bb00522a01e0513","tid":2211332,"uid":60527,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T05:17:15.000Z","msg":"自己個仔？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43d1826d347769b1f2395d1473d77859c7b9dea2","tid":2211332,"uid":77937,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T05:17:16.000Z","msg":"唔講我都唔知伍尚國"},{"pid":"e3e079fb83024132f97e689908125f58df556b53","tid":2211332,"uid":20933,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T05:17:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static-stheadline-com.cdn.ampproject.org/i/s/static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20200921/_2020092112424215787.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic-stheadline-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fi%2Fs%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20200921%2F_2020092112424215787.jpg&h=c5fb15af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n身為俗稱「速龍小隊」一員的警員伍尚國，上周五入稟高等法院，指有人在今年六6月在Facebook及Instagram上發布其相片、姓名、地址、在警隊及童軍總會的職位，意圖向他作出滋擾及恐嚇。伍要求法庭下令發布者刪除有關帖子，並要求法庭頒令禁制發布者再針對伍作出起底及滋擾行為。<br />\n<br />\n原告為伍尚國，被告為伍灝賢（英文名：Ng Ho Yin Desmond）。原告在入稟狀指被告在2020年6月6日及6月10日，透過Facebook及Instagram發佈原告的相片、姓名、地址、在警隊及童軍總會的職位，故要求法庭下令被告刪除有關資料，但禁制被告使用、發佈、傳達或披露原告的姓名、職位、住宅地址、辦公地址、電子郵件地址、出生日期、電話號碼、香港身份證號碼或其他任何官方身份證明文件的號碼、Facebook帳戶ID、Instagram帳戶ID、相片等，禁止恐嚇、騷擾、威脅或煩擾原告，禁止被告協助、造成、慫使、促致、唆使、煽動、協助、教唆或授權他人從事上述任何行為或參與上述任何行為。"},{"pid":"2cba3d46a2449b2ddbeaf7d993bde33266f3dec5","tid":2211332,"uid":147941,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T05:17:36.000Z","msg":"嘩 唔好推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8041e2dfe8bfa7f9b10ad8bba5db54d4a65db9d","tid":2211332,"uid":112748,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"fac176bd0333968bca20b9fece1ca6ce1fd23706","tid":2211332,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T05:15:02.000Z","msg":"有警員上周五（18日）入稟高等法院稱遭人「起底」，要求對方移除有關資訊，以及作出賠償。<br />\n<br />\n原告為伍尚國，被告為伍灝賢。入稟狀指出，被告今年6月6日至10日，在其facebook和Instagram發布原告的個人資料，包括中英文全名、相片、地址、警隊和童軍職級，意圖威嚇、侮辱或騷擾原告。<br />\n<br />\n原告要求被告在上述社交媒體中移除有關資訊，同時限制被告發布或公開原告的個人資料；威嚇、侮辱或騷擾原告，以及協助、鼓勵或煽惑他人作出有關行為。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T05:17:56.000Z","msg":"邊個？有無link？自已公開係FB唔係公開比人睇？我將我全部身家套現放晒係旺角行人路，然後過幾日番去囉番，唔見左就告人差唔多道理！"},{"pid":"829618919860133daa77e51120ea2b04b35f5d69","tid":2211332,"uid":36494,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T05:18:22.000Z","msg":"Google完，垃圾嚟"},{"pid":"d41f5aec88a8fc5eeb7ad7bf786c3c67de2eef64","tid":2211332,"uid":38904,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T05:19:00.000Z","msg":"個server 都唔喺香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\ndel 條撚咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"143fb7857b994819469642259f08bba7a551d1e0","tid":2211332,"uid":52881,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T05:19:03.000Z","msg":"明報咁報法,同起人底有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84c34fc4f926168c8be122018cea86c261b35f97","tid":2211332,"uid":20933,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T05:19:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hkcpgdb.com/cat8-8-4-mok6-hing3-wing4-ng5-sheung6-kwok3-common-assult.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcpgdb.com%2Fcat8-8-4-mok6-hing3-wing4-ng5-sheung6-kwok3-common-assult.html&d=nIll2RoSQXmni3IMQi%2BZoh5ZC4%2B%2BlHDPeg0yH0hWprM%3D&h=f6b38668\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcpgdb.com/cat8-8-4-mok6-hing3-wing4-ng5-sheung6-kwok3-common-assult.html</a><br />\n<br />\n綠衫莫慶榮 速龍伍尚國 另一速龍用棍襲擊街坊<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/RTHKVNEWS/videos/382871349099523/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FRTHKVNEWS%2Fvideos%2F382871349099523%2F&d=nIll2RoSQXmni3IMQi%2BZoh5ZC4%2B%2BlHDPeg0yH0hWprM%3D&h=7f1894c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/RTHKVNEWS/videos/382871349099523/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【警察追趕黑衣男子期間 另一灰衣男子被打中】<br />\n一批警察晚上在旺角警署附近，追趕一名穿黑衣的男子期間，路邊另一名穿著灰色上衣的男子，被警棍打中。<br />\n<br />\n被打中後頸的黃先生表示，當時剛從食店吃完宵夜出來，他希望警方停止暴力，形容是無差別及無逼切性。"},{"pid":"0669c35361be7bdc4856069cfe41567882e812a4","tid":2211332,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T05:20:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7bfc38db0aaa5bfd54fd4140e88792b1c24c9f6","tid":2211332,"uid":89517,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T05:21:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06c4603437d6e2ff35b556bbabb30c578d310544","tid":2211332,"uid":128102,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T05:21:54.000Z","msg":"咁搞一搞咪仲多人知道你大名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5d5d371df869868db86b90222c067d791ce39f3","tid":2211332,"uid":89517,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"47ed44eb3e99708db47e90692bb00522a01e0513","tid":2211332,"uid":60527,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T05:17:15.000Z","msg":"自己個仔？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T05:22:12.000Z","msg":"原告為伍尚國，被告為伍灝賢<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4478850057a3b13a3783901a7c365518720da446","tid":2211332,"uid":14422,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T05:22:19.000Z","msg":"老豆搵仔編號幾多號？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/fan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/fan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f741edb9bc37ab496e038756867e422d397c2418","tid":2211332,"uid":323373,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T05:22:35.000Z","msg":"想知被告係邊個?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ador