":308262,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"143fb7857b994819469642259f08bba7a551d1e0","tid":2211332,"uid":52881,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T05:19:03.000Z","msg":"明報咁報法,同起人底有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T06:17:26.000Z","msg":"明報都只係報導案情，如果佢引用老豆搵仔就唔啱<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e4140a8bb0d2e4ee8b5813fa26b9685d9090f1f","tid":2211332,"uid":194298,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e3e079fb83024132f97e689908125f58df556b53","tid":2211332,"uid":20933,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T05:17:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static-stheadline-com.cdn.ampproject.org/i/s/static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20200921/_2020092112424215787.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic-stheadline-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fi%2Fs%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20200921%2F_2020092112424215787.jpg&h=c5fb15af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n身為俗稱「速龍小隊」一員的警員伍尚國，上周五入稟高等法院，指有人在今年六6月在Facebook及Instagram上發布其相片、姓名、地址、在警隊及童軍總會的職位，意圖向他作出滋擾及恐嚇。伍要求法庭下令發布者刪除有關帖子，並要求法庭頒令禁制發布者再針對伍作出起底及滋擾行為。<br />\n<br />\n原告為伍尚國，被告為伍灝賢（英文名：Ng Ho Yin Desmond）。原告在入稟狀指被告在2020年6月6日及6月10日，透過Facebook及Instagram發佈原告的相片、姓名、地址、在警隊及童軍總會的職位，故要求法庭下令被告刪除有關資料，但禁制被告使用、發佈、傳達或披露原告的姓名、職位、住宅地址、辦公地址、電子郵件地址、出生日期、電話號碼、香港身份證號碼或其他任何官方身份證明文件的號碼、Facebook帳戶ID、Instagram帳戶ID、相片等，禁止恐嚇、騷擾、威脅或煩擾原告，禁止被告協助、造成、慫使、促致、唆使、煽動、協助、教唆或授權他人從事上述任何行為或參與上述任何行為。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T06:20:42.000Z","msg":"咁既傻鳩都做到速狗？又話飛虎特狗"},{"pid":"56f1d56a7d7d92a2a41f20316a9f858b92fb25b2","tid":2211332,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T06:20:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94240f85fd8591be20b11c0fce37be9516a04d38","tid":2211332,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T06:29:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8269f8bfff8e7690040d465fe28c1e1d43f08f08","tid":2211332,"uid":65449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T06:34:34.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"gold\">香港電台視像新聞 RTHK VNEWS<br />\n</span>2019年8月4日  &middot; <br />\n警察追趕黑衣男子期間 另一灰衣男子被打中<br />\n【警察追趕黑衣男子期間 另一灰衣男子被打中】<br />\n<br />\n一批警察晚上在旺角警署附近，追趕一名穿黑衣的男子期間，路邊另一名穿著灰色上衣的男子，被警棍打中。<br />\n<br />\n被打中後頸的黃先生表示，當時剛從食店吃完宵夜出來，他希望警方停止暴力，形容是無差別及無逼切性。<br />\n<br />\n#香港電台 #港台電視31 #港台電視32 #十點半新聞天地 #旺角 顯示較少內容"},{"pid":"c31fd4e783d31dcf0b5b69178dfce5e0fa184218","tid":2211332,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T06:37:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"129d481c199b8b6fa541d86605650130d016371e","tid":2211332,"uid":272119,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"84c34fc4f926168c8be122018cea86c261b35f97","tid":2211332,"uid":20933,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T05:19:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hkcpgdb.com/cat8-8-4-mok6-hing3-wing4-ng5-sheung6-kwok3-common-assult.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcpgdb.com%2Fcat8-8-4-mok6-hing3-wing4-ng5-sheung6-kwok3-common-assult.html&d=nIll2RoSQXmni3IMQi%2BZoh5ZC4%2B%2BlHDPeg0yH0hWprM%3D&h=f6b38668\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcpgdb.com/cat8-8-4-mok6-hing3-wing4-ng5-sheung6-kwok3-common-assult.html</a><br />\n<br />\n綠衫莫慶榮 速龍伍尚國 另一速龍用棍襲擊街坊<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/RTHKVNEWS/videos/382871349099523/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FRTHKVNEWS%2Fvideos%2F382871349099523%2F&d=nIll2RoSQXmni3IMQi%2BZoh5ZC4%2B%2BlHDPeg0yH0hWprM%3D&h=7f1894c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/RTHKVNEWS/videos/382871349099523/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【警察追趕黑衣男子期間 另一灰衣男子被打中】<br />\n一批警察晚上在旺角警署附近，追趕一名穿黑衣的男子期間，路邊另一名穿著灰色上衣的男子，被警棍打中。<br />\n<br />\n被打中後頸的黃先生表示，當時剛從食店吃完宵夜出來，他希望警方停止暴力，形容是無差別及無逼切性。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T06:37:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86c8c0eb436a6d26e1fb340da41050abd60a18e3","tid":2211332,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T06:48:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"0642550cdba98019531b0cbae78c540463494ec6","tid":2211332,"uid":20933,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T05:22:55.000Z","msg":"A171"}}